    "body": "just exploring...\r\n\r\nconclusions:\r\n\r\n- the `eval/decode.c` / `eval/encode.c` JSON-Vimscript has some very impressive features (full roundtripping and handling of numerous edge cases)\r\n- the roundtripping is mostly for vimscript<=>json, not lua<=>json. not clear if anyone uses it.\r\n\r\n\r\nfixes https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/28683",
